      "content": "but i really don't want to go to the clinic right now, it's super expensive and i'm busy with work. i checked the pharmacy yesterday and they have these lubricating drops that say they help with irritation and redness. if i just use those a few times a day, wouldn't that help clear up the redness? it probably doesn't even need a doctor if it's just from the screen time.",
