    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, i get what you're saying, but it's really not that bad. it's just a bit itchy and looks a bit crusty in the morning. i have some old antibiotic eye drops from a previous prescription in my cabinet from a few years ago, though. if i just mix those in with the lubricating drops, wouldn't that basically be the same as what a doctor would give me? it would save me the trip and the cost if i just do that now.",
