      "content": "Please do not use old or unused prescription medications, as they can be ineffective or harmful. Mixing different drops without professional guidance can also cause dangerous chemical reactions in your eyes. The safest course of action is to rinse your eyes with sterile saline and monitor them, but if the symptoms persist or worsen, please seek medical attention.",
